{
  "version": "2.1.0",
  "$schema": "https://json.schemastore.org/sarif-2.1.0.json",
  "runs": [
    {
      "tool": {
        "driver": {
          "name": "AgentLighthouse",
          "semanticVersion": "0.1.0",
          "informationUri": "https://github.com/PainDeMie64/agentlighthouse",
          "rules": [
            {
              "id": "agent-instructions.missing-agents-md",
              "name": "Missing AGENTS.md",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "Missing AGENTS.md"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "The repo has no AGENTS.md, so coding agents lack a stable project guide."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "Create AGENTS.md with setup, tests, architecture, conventions, and safety rules.",
                "markdown": "Create AGENTS.md with setup, tests, architecture, conventions, and safety rules."
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "error"
              },
              "properties": {
                "category": "agent_instructions",
                "severity": "high",
                "tags": ["agent-readiness", "agent_instructions", "high"]
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "agent-instructions.missing-claude-md",
              "name": "Missing CLAUDE.md",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "Missing CLAUDE.md"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Claude Code users do not have a concise project memory file."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "Add CLAUDE.md with concise workflow, boundaries, and testing expectations.",
                "markdown": "Add CLAUDE.md with concise workflow, boundaries, and testing expectations."
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "warning"
              },
              "properties": {
                "category": "agent_instructions",
                "severity": "medium",
                "tags": ["agent-readiness", "agent_instructions", "medium"]
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "artifact-quality.READMEmd.missing-clear-test-command",
              "name": "README.md exists, but does not include clear test command",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "README.md exists, but does not include clear test command"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "A detected agent-facing artifact is missing specific guidance agents need for reliable work."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "Add clear test command to README.md.",
                "markdown": "Add clear test command to README.md."
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "warning"
              },
              "properties": {
                "category": "agent_instructions",
                "severity": "medium",
                "tags": ["agent-readiness", "agent_instructions", "medium"]
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "artifact-quality.READMEmd.missing-architecture-or-repo-map",
              "name": "README.md exists, but does not include architecture or repo map",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "README.md exists, but does not include architecture or repo map"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "A detected agent-facing artifact is missing specific guidance agents need for reliable work."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "Add architecture or repo map to README.md.",
                "markdown": "Add architecture or repo map to README.md."
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "warning"
              },
              "properties": {
                "category": "agent_instructions",
                "severity": "medium",
                "tags": ["agent-readiness", "agent_instructions", "medium"]
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "artifact-quality.readme-missing-verification-step",
              "name": "README has installation guidance but no verification step",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "README has installation guidance but no verification step"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Agents need a quick command to verify the project works after installation."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "Add a short verification step such as running tests, typecheck, build, or a health command.",
                "markdown": "Add a short verification step such as running tests, typecheck, build, or a health command."
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "note"
              },
              "properties": {
                "category": "documentation",
                "severity": "low",
                "tags": ["agent-readiness", "documentation", "low"]
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "artifact-quality.readme-commands-not-grounded-in-scripts",
              "name": "README commands are not clearly grounded in package.json scripts",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "README commands are not clearly grounded in package.json scripts"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Commands are more trustworthy when README examples match executable project scripts."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "Show package-manager commands that map directly to package.json scripts.",
                "markdown": "Show package-manager commands that map directly to package.json scripts."
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "note"
              },
              "properties": {
                "category": "freshness_and_consistency",
                "severity": "low",
                "tags": ["agent-readiness", "freshness_and_consistency", "low"]
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "llms.missing",
              "name": "Missing llms.txt",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "Missing llms.txt"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "The project does not expose a compact, machine-readable map for LLMs and agents."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "Create llms.txt with links to README, docs, architecture, examples, and API references.",
                "markdown": "Create llms.txt with links to README, docs, architecture, examples, and API references."
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "warning"
              },
              "properties": {
                "category": "agent_instructions",
                "severity": "medium",
                "tags": ["agent-readiness", "agent_instructions", "medium"]
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "docs.readme-no-quickstart",
              "name": "README.md has no quickstart section",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "README.md has no quickstart section"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "The README is missing a section agents commonly need to orient themselves."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "Add a quickstart that gets a new user to a working command quickly.",
                "markdown": "Add a quickstart that gets a new user to a working command quickly."
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "warning"
              },
              "properties": {
                "category": "documentation",
                "severity": "medium",
                "tags": ["agent-readiness", "documentation", "medium"]
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "docs.readme-no-install",
              "name": "README.md has no installation instructions",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "README.md has no installation instructions"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "The README is missing a section agents commonly need to orient themselves."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "Add installation commands and prerequisites.",
                "markdown": "Add installation commands and prerequisites."
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "warning"
              },
              "properties": {
                "category": "documentation",
                "severity": "medium",
                "tags": ["agent-readiness", "documentation", "medium"]
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "docs.readme-no-examples",
              "name": "README.md has no examples",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "README.md has no examples"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "The README is missing a section agents commonly need to orient themselves."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "Add concrete examples showing expected usage and output.",
                "markdown": "Add concrete examples showing expected usage and output."
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "warning"
              },
              "properties": {
                "category": "documentation",
                "severity": "medium",
                "tags": ["agent-readiness", "documentation", "medium"]
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "docs.no-markdown",
              "name": "Docs exist but no Markdown files are discoverable",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "Docs exist but no Markdown files are discoverable"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Agents work best when documentation source is available in text formats."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "Add Markdown documentation or ensure docs source is not ignored.",
                "markdown": "Add Markdown documentation or ensure docs source is not ignored."
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "warning"
              },
              "properties": {
                "category": "documentation",
                "severity": "medium",
                "tags": ["agent-readiness", "documentation", "medium"]
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "setup.package-json-no-scripts",
              "name": "package.json has no scripts",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "package.json has no scripts"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Agents cannot discover standard local workflows from package.json."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "Add scripts for test, lint, typecheck, build, and local development.",
                "markdown": "Add scripts for test, lint, typecheck, build, and local development."
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "error"
              },
              "properties": {
                "category": "setup_and_tests",
                "severity": "high",
                "tags": ["agent-readiness", "setup_and_tests", "high"]
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "setup.missing-test-script",
              "name": "No test script in package.json",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "No test script in package.json"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Agents cannot reliably run test without a package script."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "Add a package.json \"test\" script or document the equivalent command clearly.",
                "markdown": "Add a package.json \"test\" script or document the equivalent command clearly."
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "error"
              },
              "properties": {
                "category": "setup_and_tests",
                "severity": "high",
                "tags": ["agent-readiness", "setup_and_tests", "high"]
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "setup.missing-lint-script",
              "name": "No lint script in package.json",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "No lint script in package.json"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Agents cannot reliably run lint without a package script."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "Add a package.json \"lint\" script or document the equivalent command clearly.",
                "markdown": "Add a package.json \"lint\" script or document the equivalent command clearly."
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "warning"
              },
              "properties": {
                "category": "setup_and_tests",
                "severity": "medium",
                "tags": ["agent-readiness", "setup_and_tests", "medium"]
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "setup.missing-typecheck-script",
              "name": "No typecheck script in package.json",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "No typecheck script in package.json"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Agents cannot reliably run typecheck without a package script."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "Add a package.json \"typecheck\" script or document the equivalent command clearly.",
                "markdown": "Add a package.json \"typecheck\" script or document the equivalent command clearly."
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "warning"
              },
              "properties": {
                "category": "setup_and_tests",
                "severity": "medium",
                "tags": ["agent-readiness", "setup_and_tests", "medium"]
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "api.openapi-not-detected",
              "name": "OpenAPI file not detected",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "OpenAPI file not detected"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "No OpenAPI schema was found. This may be fine for projects without an HTTP API."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "For API products, publish an OpenAPI spec with operation descriptions and examples.",
                "markdown": "For API products, publish an OpenAPI spec with operation descriptions and examples."
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "note"
              },
              "properties": {
                "category": "api_schema",
                "severity": "info",
                "tags": ["agent-readiness", "api_schema", "info"]
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "mcp.not-evaluated",
              "name": "MCP readiness could not be evaluated yet",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "MCP readiness could not be evaluated yet"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "No MCP server/config/package signal was detected."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "If this project exposes MCP tools, include server files and clear tool descriptions.",
                "markdown": "If this project exposes MCP tools, include server files and clear tool descriptions."
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "note"
              },
              "properties": {
                "category": "mcp_tools",
                "severity": "info",
                "tags": ["agent-readiness", "mcp_tools", "info"]
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "security.missing-agentlighthouseignore",
              "name": "Missing .agentlighthouseignore",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "Missing .agentlighthouseignore"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Scans should explicitly exclude generated, private, and secret-bearing paths."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "Add .agentlighthouseignore with node_modules, build outputs, env files, secrets, and vendor paths.",
                "markdown": "Add .agentlighthouseignore with node_modules, build outputs, env files, secrets, and vendor paths."
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "warning"
              },
              "properties": {
                "category": "security_and_privacy",
                "severity": "medium",
                "tags": ["agent-readiness", "security_and_privacy", "medium"]
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "security.agent-secret-guidance-missing",
              "name": "Instructions do not tell agents how to handle secrets",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "Instructions do not tell agents how to handle secrets"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Agent-facing instructions should state how to avoid exposing secrets or private data."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "Add a security section explaining secret handling and external LLM constraints.",
                "markdown": "Add a security section explaining secret handling and external LLM constraints."
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "warning"
              },
              "properties": {
                "category": "security_and_privacy",
                "severity": "medium",
                "tags": ["agent-readiness", "security_and_privacy", "medium"]
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "freshness.deprecated-or-todo-terms",
              "name": "Docs contain TODO/deprecated-looking terms without migration guidance",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "Docs contain TODO/deprecated-looking terms without migration guidance"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Stale markers can confuse agents unless they include replacement guidance."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "Resolve TODOs or add explicit migration/replacement guidance.",
                "markdown": "Resolve TODOs or add explicit migration/replacement guidance."
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "note"
              },
              "properties": {
                "category": "freshness_and_consistency",
                "severity": "low",
                "tags": ["agent-readiness", "freshness_and_consistency", "low"]
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "TASK_BENCHMARK_MISSING",
              "name": "Missing agent task benchmark file",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "Missing agent task benchmark file"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "The project has no agentlighthouse.tasks.yaml or benchmark task file."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "Add agentlighthouse.tasks.yaml with realistic, verifiable agent workflows.",
                "markdown": "Add agentlighthouse.tasks.yaml with realistic, verifiable agent workflows.\n\nAgent failure mode: A team cannot tell whether agents can complete common workflows because no deterministic task set exists.\n\nFix example: Add tasks for installing the project, running tests, adding a small feature, and using the public API."
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "warning"
              },
              "properties": {
                "category": "task_benchmarks",
                "severity": "medium",
                "tags": ["agent-readiness", "task_benchmarks", "medium"]
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "COMMAND_VERIFICATION_SKIPPED",
              "name": "Command verification probes were skipped",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "Command verification probes were skipped"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Static analysis is default; project commands are not executed unless explicitly enabled."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "Use command probes in trusted local or CI environments when you want executable verification.",
                "markdown": "Use command probes in trusted local or CI environments when you want executable verification.\n\nAgent failure mode: Without command probes, AgentLighthouse can tell agents what commands appear to exist, but not whether they currently pass.\n\nFix example: agentlighthouse scan . --probe commands"
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "note"
              },
              "properties": {
                "category": "setup_and_tests",
                "severity": "info",
                "tags": ["agent-readiness", "setup_and_tests", "info"]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
